message.body: Hey, wanna meet at tla tonight or something else? Did you see doors are at 10? Fair warning, I might fall asleep standing up!
Uh oh! We were just thinking maybe something to eat before? Waiting for Charlie to get here to finalize. What do you think?
I like it! I'm not sure how long Richard is gonna be at work though. Percy st BBQ is near there, I like that place. Keep me posted!
That sounds good. I'll check it out. We can stay in touch and maybe meet there.
Roger that! They have many beers in cans & craft root beer if we're too late for dinner too.
Hey, Cour and I just parked headed into Percy st. BBQ at 900 south.
K. We'll meet ya there. Julia, let me know when your headed over and we can figure stuff out.
I think we'll get there around 9, I'll see where you're at when we're close!
Great, text when your near and I'll update you as to our where abouts.
Slight detour in plans. Denise needs to take care of her dog. Let us know where you land.
Just settled in at Percy st :)
On our way to the TLA now.
